title: 01/07/22 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 01/07/22 DPS Best Of
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to Sean Salisbury about who he'd prefer as his QB, Baker Mayfield or Kirk Cousins? Nets Play by Play announcer Ian Eagle discusses whether KD and Kyrie's friendship has been fractured or gotten stronger this season. And Tampa Bay area Radio Host Tom Krasniqi shares what the local coverage of Antonio Brown has been like.
